[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "The laborer is counted as the most material and egoistical man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "To this the humane liberal retorts: The unsettledness of many is only your product, Philistine!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "But what are they to do with their leisure?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "It is assuredly necessary that man be masterless: but therefore the egoist is not to become master over man again either, but man over the egoist.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "But you laborers undertake even your labor from an egoistic impulse, because you want to eat, drink, live; how should you be less egoists in leisure?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "This alone is human, because only Man is disinterested, the egoist always interested.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "On the contrary!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Further: The Jew, the Christian, the privileged person, the theologian, etc, is not a human being; so far as you are a Jew, etc, you are not a human being.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Again the imperious postulate: Cast from you everything peculiar, criticise it away!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "I say: You are indeed more than a Jew, more than a Christian, etc, but you are also more than a human being.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Those are all ideas, but you are corporeal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Do you suppose our posterity will find no prejudices and limits to clear away, for which our powers were not sufficient?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000012_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000012_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "What do you need that later liberty for?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000012_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000012_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "But, as you will surely die before that, what becomes of your prize of victory?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "In the second place, as a Jew one assuredly cannot be a man, if being a man means being nothing special.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000014_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000014_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Is it otherwise with the Jews of to day?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000014_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000014_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Because you have discovered the idea of humanity, does it follow from this that every Jew can become a convert to it?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000014_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000014_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "What does your demand concern him?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "As a universal principle, in the \"human society\" which the humane liberal promises, nothing \"special\" which one or another has is to find recognition, nothing which bears the character of \"private\" is to have value.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Because State and society do not suffice for humane liberalism, it negates both, and at the same time retains them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "So at one time the cry is that the task of the day is \"not a political, but a social, one,\" and then again the \"free State\" is promised for the future.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Both are to leave private interests to private people, and, as human society, concern themselves solely about general human interests.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "In this supreme development of \"free man\" egoism, self ownership, is combated on principle, and such subordinate ends as the social \"welfare\" of the Socialists, etc, vanish before the lofty \"idea of humanity.\" Everything that is not a \"general human\" entity is something separate, satisfies only some or one; or, if it satisfies all, it does this to them only as individuals, not as men, and is therefore called \"egoistic.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000024_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000024_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "For man is mind: therefore all powers that are alien to him, the mind,--all superhuman, heavenly, unhuman powers,--must be overthrown, and the name \"man\" must be above every name.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "So in this end of the modern age (age of the moderns) there returns again, as the main point, what had been the main point at its beginning: \"intellectual liberty.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Laboring does not alone make you a man, because it is something formal and its object accidental; the question is who you that labor are.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "The laborer has still remaining the desire for a \"higher consciousness,\" which, because the activity of labor is unable to quiet it, he satisfies in a leisure hour.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "His labor ought to satisfy him as a man; instead of that, it satisfies society; society ought to treat him as a man, and it treats him as-a rag tag laborer, or a laboring ragamuffin.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Labor and society are of use to him not as he needs them as a man, but only as he needs them as an \"egoist.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Such is the attitude of criticism toward labor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "Therefore humane liberalism says: You want labor; all right, we want it likewise, but we want it in the fullest measure.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6084_2159_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6084/2159/6084_2159_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6084",
        "content": "This restless mind is the true laborer, it obliterates prejudices, shatters limits and narrownesses, and raises man above everything that would like to dominate over him, while the Communist labors only for himself, and not even freely, but from necessity,--in short, represents a man condemned to hard labor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    }
]